title: Episode 1 w/ Guest Fat Joe
itunes:title: Episode 1 w/ Guest Fat Joe
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN drink it up with hip hop legend Fat Joe. The guys talk about Fat Joe's new collaborative project with Remy Ma, and the process he underwent in making the album. Fat Joe also goes into various untold hip hop stories. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
